<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Sumo-Squat">Dumbbell Sumo Squat</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-sumo-squat" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Dumbbell sumo squats</a> are an effective variation of the classic squat that targets multiple lower body muscles, especially the glutes. The wider stance and outward-pointing toes promote greater activation of both the <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33477561/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">gluteus maximus</a> and gluteus medius.</p>



<p>This exercise not only works the glutes but also engages the inner thighs, or adductors, more than traditional squats. The sumo stance challenges these muscles, contributing to overall lower body strength and definition.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="Dumbbell Sumo Squat" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1000637285?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write"></iframe>
</div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Dumbbell Sumo Squat Guide. Video: Aliaksandr Makatserchyk</figcaption></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How To Do</h4>



<ol>
<li>Stand with feet about one-a-half times the shoulder-width, toes pointed outward.</li>



<li>Hold a dumbbell between your legs with both hands.</li>



<li>Lower your body by bending your knees and hips simultaneously, keeping your back straight and upright.</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips</h4>



<ul>
<li>Push through your feet and squeeze your glutes on your way up.</li>



<li>Keep your chest up and maintain the core engagement.</li>



<li>Focus on feeling the activation in your glutes and inner thighs during each repetition.</li>
</ul>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Optimal Sets And Reps</h4>



<div class="wp-block-group medicine-table is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
